library(magick)
#create a box for text 
under_square1 <- image_blank(w=300,
                             h=250,
                             c="#e6ffe6")%>%
  image_annotate(text = "the first time i learn how to \nPrint 'Hello world'",
                 color = "#000000"
                   ,size = 20
                 ,font = "Impact"
                 ,gravity = "center")

#call the meme i find 
meme1 <- image_read("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQlSaA818mIMKGl1p6ecgq38eIHZSCua_zG7A&usqp=CAU")%>%
  image_resize("300x250!")

pr1 <- image_append(c(meme1,under_square1))

under_square2 <- image_blank(w=300,
                             h=300,
                             c="#e6ffe6")%>%
  image_annotate(text = "when i start to work on my own ",
                 color = "#000000",
                 size = 20,
                 font = "Impact"
                 ,gravity = "center")

meme2 <- image_read("https://global.discourse-cdn.com/codecademy/original/5X/3/c/8/5/3c85feecb4eb52a4d69ef0891cfbc495a1da7174.png")%>%
  image_resize("300x300!")

pr2 <- image_append(c(meme2,under_square2))

final_meme <- image_append(c(pr1,pr2),stack = TRUE)
image_write(final_meme, "CS_student.png")

library(magick)
#create a box for text 
under_square1 <- image_blank(w=300,
                             h=250,
                             c="#e6ffe6")%>%
  image_annotate(text = "the first time i learn how to \nPrint 'Hello world'",
                 color = "#000000"
                   ,size = 20
                 ,font = "Impact"
                 ,gravity = "center")

#call the meme i find 
meme1 <- image_read("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQlSaA818mIMKGl1p6ecgq38eIHZSCua_zG7A&usqp=CAU")%>%
  image_resize("300x250!")%>%
  image_convert("png")

pr1 <- image_append(c(meme1,under_square1))

#create a box2 for text
under_square2 <- image_blank(w=300,
                             h=300,
                             c="#e6ffe6")%>%
  image_annotate(text = "when i start to work on my own ",
                 color = "#000000",
                 size = 20,
                 font = "Impact"
                 ,gravity = "center")

#call the memew i find 
meme2 <- image_read("https://global.discourse-cdn.com/codecademy/original/5X/3/c/8/5/3c85feecb4eb52a4d69ef0891cfbc495a1da7174.png")%>%
  image_resize("300x300!")%>%
  image_convert("png")

#put togeter
frames <- c(under_square1, meme1, under_square2, meme2) 
ans <- image_morph(frames)%>%
  image_animate(fps = 100)
#save as gif
image_write(ans, "CS_study.gif")
